metadata.name: #1 Botanic Poppy
metadata.description:
This  is a photo version inspired by botanical illustrations.
She tried to reproduce it in the 3D world, drawing inspiration from the botanical illustrations that she had been familiar with since childhood.

She chose flowers herself, layout them and shoot then completed a unique world view that is different from traditional botanical illustrations.
The shape of the petals and roots is also included in the design.

3000 x2000
350dpi
